  "id": "RAW_52fc63a7",
  "title": "一家中国科技公司，正在用 AI 创造世界杯观赛的新模式",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjc1NjM3MjY2MA==&mid=2691569308&idx=1&sn=d698615556b46153ee42ebe2c1b0cdde",
  "date": "2026-06-14 17:58:00",
  "author": "腾讯科技",
  "siteName": "腾讯科技",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4be4e89f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FQmK3dYQtkw3J3CWKKiamOcLHwRIxIsBpicXhDuNzQDJ0VVcibUo0cU8QzFyoicAWEZM9Hkm5pFzTjWibus9BEbmosvQa6wcIXAVK24dXgUQdXWsM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; text-align: center; width: 100%;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">文｜吴彬</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">编辑｜徐青阳</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当地时间6月11日，世界杯揭幕战墨西哥队 vs 南非队第9分钟，墨西哥队打入本届赛事首球。对于全球观众来说，这只是比赛中的一个瞬间。但这一次，人们看到的不只是传统转播画面，裁判佩戴摄像头拍摄的第一视角画面同步出现在直播信号中，球迷第一次能够从裁判的视角观察比赛。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这样的画面能够出现在世界杯赛场，背后连接着AI视频增强、实时数据处理、赛事运营系统以及全球转播网络。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果说过去几届世界杯的技术创新更多集中在转播和传播环节，2026年这届出现了一个新的变化：AI开始进入赛事运行本身，从裁判辅助判罚、比赛分析，到赛事组织和球迷互动。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">联想集团，是这些技术体系背后的贡献者之一。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">01&nbsp;</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">一届前所未有的世界杯</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2026年世界杯本身已经足够特殊。这是世界杯历史上首次扩军至48支球队，首次由美国、加拿大和墨西哥三国联合举办，整个赛事覆盖16座城市，共进行104场比赛。联想方面援引独立科技研究机构未尽研究的预测：全球约有60亿观众关注本届世界杯，决赛当天预计约有20亿人同时收看。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">赛事规模扩大，意味着技术系统面临的压力同步增加。比赛场馆分散在三个国家，赛事内容需要面向全球传播，海量视频、数据和互动信息持续产生。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7edb3b8e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FQmK3dYQtkw2ydDeqHb5lCHF3SKeG6lwxLu2CbAxOdTqD9aial0FQonVSvELhmxVkBJNUsAOSkt4ZfO6R4OrmKn7hK83vyRvw2Bzt0FAhBdmc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">联想集团副总裁、SSG业务应用服务交付部负责人陈敏仪</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">6月11日，在腾讯新闻于墨西哥城举办的「寻梦之夜：文明与智能」沙龙上，联想集团副总裁、SSG业务应用服务交付部负责人陈敏仪提到一个判断：</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">2026年世界杯有可能成为AI技术落地规模最大的一次体育赛事实践。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">回顾世界杯近百年历史，每一次重要技术进步都改变了人们参与赛事的方式。广播让远方的人第一次“听见世界杯”，电视把比赛带进家庭，高清转播让观众看清赛场细节，互联网和社交媒体让观赛从单向传播变成全球互动。而今天，AI开始影响的不再只是“怎么看”，更是“怎么踢”和“怎么评”。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">02&nbsp;</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">AI技术如何介入赛事运行</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">足球是最复杂的团队运动之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">场上22名球员持续高速移动，比赛节奏不断变化，裁判单场比赛需要做出超过200次判罚决策，每一个决策窗口以秒甚至毫秒计算。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">本届世界杯进一步放大了这种难度，赛事跨越三国举行，比赛密集，全球数十亿观众同时关注，技术系统不仅要准确，更要稳定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">本届世界杯最受关注的创新之一，是裁判视角摄像头。</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">开幕战中，观众首次通过裁判的第一视角观看比赛。裁判在场上高速移动，视角剧烈变化，原始画面的抖动和模糊程度远超固定机位拍摄。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a667b8ee&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FQmK3dYQtkw1w3uMEbom9kVNLGt8fGMW5jdPCveflLzGSHAs3uy55UiaJhndSVOib3vKA6DDibj2P5UcO9ezLX0gvzJolAATpbCMAHvh1g4gFCM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">联想为此开发了裁判视角AI视频增强系统，通过AI驱动的影像稳定增强技术，在毫秒级延迟内对画面进行实时平滑处理，将高动态运动场景下的画面失真降低高达50%。这不是一个后期处理问题，而是一个实时计算问题——系统必须在画面产生的同时完成处理，且不能影响直播信号的同步性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">相比观众能直接看到的转播创新，更多技术工作发生在幕后。联想通过数十万张人体数据训练算法，为1248名参赛球员全自动生成3D数字人模型，用于比赛分析和判罚辅助。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5b3c17b8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQmK3dYQtkw2urj5V19RicFoU3xD5OyzUpSvNpibyyYVhXxvkANhE2JyPfKe2fWT2YgyAibx2qhZqqN8VR5MeZG08MhfSK2EXJuicwOzF9CLBEWk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这套方案改变了越位判断的技术基础。过去VAR依赖二维画面，裁判需要从有限的摄像机角度判断球员位置，存在视角盲区和透视误差；3D模型则可以在三维空间中还原球员的精确位置和运动轨迹，从根本上减少角度限制带来的误判风险。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=01c288be&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FQmK3dYQtkw2HgpFuuzzGkrh03XLcs3Q5cal0RwNhSBgn4tEUqojDZxbqLKLxdkJ0OvbZXpqDvAvsvEzQmR7R6oekrQAqaNJwwORlKANtSuY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px